  - `pages/UserSetting/Payment&Wallet/payment&wallet.jsx` and `pages/UserSetting/Wishlist/wishlist.jsx` already consume `profileApi.js`, `walletApi.js`, and `publicPackagesApi.js`, so those current-user v1 clients are part of the active protected flow baseline
- Backend support and verification surface:
