+### 2026-03-09 - Phase 3 Implement Highest-Priority Batch (`full-enhance`, run `20260309-205940-full-enhance`)
+
+#### Implemented Batch
+- Batch A landed as planned:
+  - `SUP-ROUTE-001`
+  - `SUP-UX-001`
+  - `SUP-API-001`
+- Concrete implementation outcome:
+  - added a protected `/help` route and `help.jsx` route owner backed by `supportApi.js` current-user complaint/request history
+  - removed detached `/reviews` account navigation from both `sidebar.jsx` and `Header.js`; reviews now submit contextually from `/operator-response`
